<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:x-large;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>The Final Ascension</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> or perhaps The Apocalypse.  <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:large;">July 6th!!</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
<br>
I come forth for what will be perhaps the final time to offer my personal invitation to members of Fire and Fury with whom I have been friends past to the ceremony that will send my Heavenly spirit home forever.  I will be awake for most of the day to say personal goodbyes, and at the conclution of the ceremony at the listed time, I will never again be able to walk in your mortal lands.  =(<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What?:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> The Ascension of Ayrielle into Heaven.  Her final moment in this world.  Perhaps even the final moment of the entire world.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Where?:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> The Greater Faydark Moon Spires.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>When?:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> 7 in the evening as according to Eastern Standard Time of Kelethin<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>For Who?:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> For all, both good and evil.  There will likely be something to please all.<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>What should I do?:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> <br>
--- You are present at the aforementioned time.  (You may wish to come early, as the time is precise.  If you wish to say goodbyes, come even earlier, because once the ceremony begins, there will be no time.)<br>
--- You listen in on what is happening within two rooms for chatting:<br>
<br>
Chatting room one - Ayrielle (This room should be viewed as light blue)<br>
Chatting room two - FallenAngel (This room should be viewed as red)<br>
<br>
--- You take a copy of the sheet music here and be prepared to give it to the orchestra when the directions are given.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/silentayrielle/Act_I.mp3" target="top">Act I</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/silentayrielle/Act_II.mp3" target="top">Act II</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/silentayrielle/Act_III.mp3" target="top">Act III</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
You may need to copy down the name of the room these sheets are in and enter them upon your own.  I apoligize for my lack of knowledge for how to properly direct you about.  =(<br>
<br>
I would offer advise and say that you may not wish to sample the music beforehand lest you perhaps spoil a surprise or two.  =)<br>
<br>
<br>
---  You make the emotions and actions of others very clear in your eyes.  Although you will not want to view them in the same colors as the two chatting rooms.<br>
---  You agree that you will not interfere in the ceremony once begin.  Please refrain from casting spells or speaking too loud.  No matter what happens, please do not interfere, even to help.  Please do not fight amongst yourselves either once the ceremony is under way.<br>
<br>
I highly advise you to prepare for the orchestra.  It will be very much worth your efforts, and without such, you will not even begin to experince all there is to offer.  =)  At this time there are three (a First, Second, and Third) songs that will be played in succession.<br>
<br>
This is for any and all to attend.  If you believe yourself to walk in the light, you will witness an angel returning to her true home of Heaven.<br>
<br>
If you believe yourself to walk in the darkness, there is a dark omen surrounding this night.  If the prophecies I have studied up on in recent weeks are to be believed, the powers you stand behind will come forth in furious strenght, and the entire world of Norrath may well be destroyed in the process.  I will give you a glimpse into what may unfold as foretold:<br>
